TopicTitle: Half my mods not loading, were all installed via ckan. What gives?!

Articles.Content:
Using CKAN to manage my mods, on Mac OSX 10.11.4, KSP 1.1.2.  Trying to get Stock Visual Enhancements and ScienceAlert going, can't figure out why they're not working!  The other mods seem to be loading fine...SVE was installed by CKAN, ScienceAlert I installed manually.

http://imgur.com/a/JhUbD
Science Alert isn't compatible with 1.1+ Remove it until its updated.
